# ===== SuitesForAll .gitignore =====================================
# Established 2026-05-01 alongside the project's first commit.
# Goal: keep the repo small + free of secrets, machine state, and
# anything regenerable.

# --- Dependency directories ---
node_modules/
functions/node_modules/

# --- Firebase tooling cache ---
# Local emulator state, deploy hashes, cached function artifacts.
# Safe to delete; recreated on next `firebase deploy` / `emulators:start`.
.firebase/
firebase-debug.log
firebase-debug.*.log
*.firebase.json.bak

# --- macOS / FUSE / IDE noise ---
.DS_Store
.fuse_hidden*
*.swp
*.swo
.idea/
.vscode/
*.sublime-workspace

# --- Build output / logs ---
dist/
build/
*.log
npm-debug.log*

# --- Local environment / secrets ---
# The repo holds .firebaserc (project ID only — public) but anything
# resembling .env should never be committed.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
serviceAccount*.json

# --- Temp scratch screenshots from lease-document iteration ---
# These were exported during DocuSign signature design experiments and
# aren't referenced by the live app. Keeping them out of git keeps the
# repo lean (each is 50–200 KB).
_lease-*.jpg
_v-*.jpg
_body-*.jpg
_sig-verify*.jpg
_body-verify*.jpg
